OL,1,U5|j5pp0up`pp0s1z0ppp      W h54  j  
OL,2,U5j5{57js15k!w      W 5$  j  
OL,3,U}~5|4}h|55j }|      Wh2-l|,&  
OL,4,E`````````````````````````````W*7<=mE`
OL,5,BTHE STORY OF SUPER PAGE 58    W!/////  
OL,6,B                                       
OL,7,F"Chris Bell's website is about some-   
OL,8,Fthing called Digitiser. I'm not sure   
OL,9,Fwhat that is, but his links page is    
OL,10,Fgood - it looks like a real website."  
OL,11,B                                       
OL,12,BThese were the first words ever written
OL,13,BaboutESuper Page 58B- one of the very  
OL,14,Bfirst Digitiser fansites - inEDecember 
OL,15,E1997.                                  
OL,16,B                                       
OL,17,BThose slightly flummoxed words came    
OL,18,Bfrom the classmate who was assigned to 
OL,19,Breview it as part of the uni assignment
OL,20,E``````````````````````````````````1/20`
OL,21,             BBy Chris Bell             
OL,22,D]MG    TELETEXT ART SHOWCASE p104      
OL,24,AAboutBUser GuideCTeletext ArtFMainIndex
PN,10602
SC,0002
FL,102,103,104,101,4ff,100
OL,1,U5|j5pp0up`pp0s1z0ppp      W h54  j  
OL,2,U5j5{57js15k!w      W 5$  j  
OL,3,U}~5|4}h|55j }|      Wh2-l|,&  
OL,4,E`````````````````````````````W*7<=mE`
OL,5,BTHE STORY OF SUPER PAGE 58    W!/////  
OL,6,B                                       
OL,7,ESuper Page 58Bstarted out as a quick   
OL,8,Buniversity assignment, you see - the   
OL,9,Bwhole class had to make their own site.
OL,10,B                                       
OL,11,BI had to review someone else's. No idea
OL,12,Bwhose or what it was like. Or whether  
OL,13,Bit's still online nearly 22 years later
OL,14,B                                       
OL,15,E22 years.BCrikey. Like anyone ever saw 
OL,16,Bthat coming! Certainly not me: I didn't
OL,17,Beven think to tell Digi it was online! 
OL,18,B                                       
OL,19,B                                       
OL,20,E``````````````````````````````````2/20`
OL,21,             BBy Chris Bell             
OL,22,D]MG    TELETEXT ART SHOWCASE p104      
OL,24,AAboutBUser GuideCTeletext ArtFMainIndex
PN,10603
SC,0003
FL,102,103,104,101,4ff,100
OL,1,U5|j5pp0up`pp0s1z0ppp      W h54  j  
OL,2,U5j5{57js15k!w      W 5$  j  
OL,3,U}~5|4}h|55j }|      Wh2-l|,&  
OL,4,E`````````````````````````````W*7<=mE`
OL,5,BTHE STORY OF SUPER PAGE 58    W!/////  
OL,6,B                                       
OL,7,BIt was my sister who thought me having 
OL,8,BaEDigitiser websiteBwas worth telling  
OL,9,BDigitiser about.                       
OL,10,B                                       
OL,11,BAfter she'd written to tell them, Biffo
OL,12,Bemailed me. That was quite a shock to  
OL,13,Bsee. The man was practically aEhero of 
OL,14,Emythological legend.BYet here he was   
OL,15,Bwriting to me.                         
OL,16,B                                       
OL,17,BMy website was out in the wild now. One
OL,18,Bmention on Digi later, andEmy destiny  
OL,19,Bwas set. I had to keep it running.     
OL,20,E``````````````````````````````````3/20`
OL,21,             BBy Chris Bell             
OL,22,D]MG    TELETEXT ART SHOWCASE p104      
OL,24,AAboutBUser GuideCTeletext ArtFMainIndex
PN,10604
SC,0004
FL,102,103,104,101,4ff,100
OL,1,U5|j5pp0up`pp0s1z0ppp      W h54  j  
OL,2,U5j5{57js15k!w      W 5$  j  
OL,3,U}~5|4}h|55j }|      Wh2-l|,&  
OL,4,E`````````````````````````````W*7<=mE`
OL,5,BTHE STORY OF SUPER PAGE 58    W!/////  
OL,6,B                                       
OL,7,BThe irony was that I had only ever     
OL,8,Bwritten a letter to Digitiser once, all
OL,9,Bthe way back in theEspring of 1994.    
OL,10,B                                       
OL,11,BI wasn't part of any community at this 
OL,12,Bpoint. The letter was written defending
OL,13,BDigi for the flack they'd been getting 
OL,14,BasE"Sega-sceptics".                    
OL,15,B                                       
OL,16,BThe Mega Drive was struggling to keep  
OL,17,Bup with the times compared to the SNES,
OL,18,BI wrote. In typical Digi style, they   
OL,19,Bcompletely disagreed with me in reply. 
OL,20,E``````````````````````````````````4/20`
OL,21,             BBy Chris Bell             
OL,22,D]MG    TELETEXT ART SHOWCASE p104      
OL,24,AAboutBUser GuideCTeletext ArtFMainIndex
PN,10605
SC,0005
FL,102,103,104,101,4ff,100
OL,1,U5|j5pp0up`pp0s1z0ppp      W h54  j  
OL,2,U5j5{57js15k!w      W 5$  j  
OL,3,U}~5|4}h|55j }|      Wh2-l|,&  
OL,4,E`````````````````````````````W*7<=mE`
OL,5,BTHE STORY OF SUPER PAGE 58    W!/////  
OL,6,B                                       
OL,7,BI was alwaysEimmensely gratefulBfor the
OL,8,Bpositive mentions the site would get on
OL,9,BDigi from time to time.                
OL,10,B                                       
OL,11,BI never went asking for plugs, so it   
OL,12,Bmade me "laugh" when I received a livid
OL,13,Bemail from anEalt.digitiserBregular    
OL,14,Blambasting me for sending newbies there
OL,15,Bvia my links page, because I'd begged  
OL,16,Bfor mentions.                          
OL,17,B                                       
OL,18,BI put a disclaimer on the link to the  
OL,19,Bnewsgroup after that...                
OL,20,E``````````````````````````````````5/20`
OL,21,             BBy Chris Bell             
OL,22,D]MG    TELETEXT ART SHOWCASE p104      
OL,24,AAboutBUser GuideCTeletext ArtFMainIndex
PN,10606
SC,0006
FL,102,103,104,101,4ff,100
OL,1,U5|j5pp0up`pp0s1z0ppp      W h54  j  
OL,2,U5j5{57js15k!w      W 5$  j  
OL,3,U}~5|4}h|55j }|      Wh2-l|,&  
OL,4,E`````````````````````````````W*7<=mE`
OL,5,BTHE STORY OF SUPER PAGE 58    W!/////  
OL,6,B                                       
OL,7,BBecause of its accidental origins, I'd 
OL,8,Bnever really had a plan or target for  
OL,9,Bwhat I wanted to do with Super Page 58.
OL,10,BAs a result, I letEDigi's readersBsteer
OL,11,Bthat for me.                           
OL,12,B                                       
OL,13,BPeople emailed me fairly regularly, and
OL,14,Bmany would ask for certain content.    
OL,15,BI did what I could - but I didn't have 
OL,16,Ba TV card to save teletext images, and 
OL,17,Bthere was concern among the fansite    
OL,18,Bcommunity aboutEcopyright infringement 
OL,19,Banyway.                                
OL,20,E``````````````````````````````````6/20`
OL,21,             BBy Chris Bell             
OL,22,D]MG    TELETEXT ART SHOWCASE p104      
OL,24,AAboutBUser GuideCTeletext ArtFMainIndex
PN,10607
SC,0007
FL,102,103,104,101,4ff,100
OL,1,U5|j5pp0up`pp0s1z0ppp      W h54  j  
OL,2,U5j5{57js15k!w      W 5$  j  
OL,3,U}~5|4}h|55j }|      Wh2-l|,&  
OL,4,E`````````````````````````````W*7<=mE`
OL,5,BTHE STORY OF SUPER PAGE 58    W!/////  
OL,6,B                                       
OL,7,BThe one thing that stood out head and  
OL,8,Bshoulders above other content requests 
OL,9,Bwas a desire for aEMan Diary archiveB- 
OL,10,Bthey'd never been saved anywhere       
OL,11,Bbefore.                                
OL,12,B                                       
OL,13,BSo many people asked for it in the end,
OL,14,Bthat I duly obliged.                   
OL,15,B                                       
OL,16,BAs a consequence of not having the kit 
OL,17,Bto save it, I took toEtranscribing the 
OL,18,EMan Diaries by hand,Bthen painstakingly
OL,19,Btyping them up. That took dedication!  
OL,20,E``````````````````````````````````7/20`
OL,21,             BBy Chris Bell             
OL,22,D]MG    TELETEXT ART SHOWCASE p104      
OL,24,AAboutBUser GuideCTeletext ArtFMainIndex
PN,10608
SC,0008
FL,102,103,104,101,4ff,100
OL,1,U5|j5pp0up`pp0s1z0ppp      W h54  j  
OL,2,U5j5{57js15k!w      W 5$  j  
OL,3,U}~5|4}h|55j }|      Wh2-l|,&  
OL,4,E`````````````````````````````W*7<=mE`
OL,5,BTHE STORY OF SUPER PAGE 58    W!/////  
OL,6,B                                       
OL,7,BAs Super Page 58 grew and I added more 
OL,8,Bcontent, it began to attract more and  
OL,9,Bmore attention. Not all of it welcome. 
OL,10,B                                       
OL,11,BIn early 2001 I received a belligerent-
OL,12,Bly wordedElegal emailBfrom the absurdly
OL,13,Bdouble-surname-named lawyer for the    
OL,14,Bpublishers of theEBluffer's GuideBbooks
OL,15,B                                       
OL,16,BWhat is now theE"Do You See?"Bsection  
OL,17,Bused to be called the Bluffer's Guide  
OL,18,BTo Digi. Apparently I was a Bad Man who
OL,19,Bsought to profit from their name!      
OL,20,E``````````````````````````````````8/20`
OL,21,             BBy Chris Bell             
OL,22,D]MG    TELETEXT ART SHOWCASE p104      
OL,24,AAboutBUser GuideCTeletext ArtFMainIndex
PN,10609
SC,0009
FL,102,103,104,101,4ff,100
OL,1,U5|j5pp0up`pp0s1z0ppp      W h54  j  
OL,2,U5j5{57js15k!w      W 5$  j  
OL,3,U}~5|4}h|55j }|      Wh2-l|,&  
OL,4,E`````````````````````````````W*7<=mE`
OL,5,BTHE STORY OF SUPER PAGE 58    W!/////  
OL,6,B                                       
OL,7,B2001 was a significant year for Digi.  
OL,8,BIt had been enjoying something of a    
OL,9,Egolden period:BThe Snakes and Mr T were
OL,10,Briding high, and the Digitiser Donkey  
OL,11,Bwas making an impression on the letters
OL,12,Bpage.                                  
OL,13,B                                       
OL,14,BWhich was great. Except:EI didn't get  
OL,15,Eto see much of it.BMy family was moving
OL,16,BMum had cancelled the phone, and my    
OL,17,Binternet access with it. We didn't even
OL,18,Bmove for another six months. And there 
OL,19,Bstopped the regular site updates...    
OL,20,E``````````````````````````````````9/20`
OL,21,             BBy Chris Bell             
OL,22,D]MG    TELETEXT ART SHOWCASE p104      
OL,24,AAboutBUser GuideCTeletext ArtFMainIndex
PN,10610
SC,0010
FL,102,103,104,101,4ff,100
OL,1,U5|j5pp0up`pp0s1z0ppp      W h54  j  
OL,2,U5j5{57js15k!w      W 5$  j  
OL,3,U}~5|4}h|55j }|      Wh2-l|,&  
OL,4,E`````````````````````````````W*7<=mE`
OL,5,BTHE STORY OF SUPER PAGE 58    W!/////  
OL,6,B                                       
OL,7,BSite updates ended in theEsummer of    
OL,8,E2001,Beven though I got my internet    
OL,9,Baccess back the following January.     
OL,10,B                                       
OL,11,BThe reason?EDigigate had happened.     
OL,12,BSuffice to say, the Digitiser that was 
OL,13,Bon the air now was a sad shadow of its 
OL,14,Bformer self. Teletext Ltd had claimed  
OL,15,BDigi's humour "excluded" people, when  
OL,16,Bin fact the reverse was true.          
OL,17,B                                       
OL,18,BI couldn't bring myself to read Digi   
OL,19,Bagain until theEend of 2002.           
OL,20,E`````````````````````````````````10/20`
OL,21,             BBy Chris Bell             
OL,22,D]MG    TELETEXT ART SHOWCASE p104      
OL,24,AAboutBUser GuideCTeletext ArtFMainIndex
PN,10611
SC,0011
FL,102,103,104,101,4ff,100
OL,1,U5|j5pp0up`pp0s1z0ppp      W h54  j  
OL,2,U5j5{57js15k!w      W 5$  j  
OL,3,U}~5|4}h|55j }|      Wh2-l|,&  
OL,4,E`````````````````````````````W*7<=mE`
OL,5,BTHE STORY OF SUPER PAGE 58    W!/////  
OL,6,B                                       
OL,7,BJust before Digigate, I'd started a new
OL,8,Bjob, and had a work email account for  
OL,9,Bfirst time. Offline for months at home,
OL,10,Bone of the first things I did was to   
OL,11,Bemail Biffo.                           
OL,12,B                                       
OL,13,BThe timing was impeccable - he told me 
OL,14,Bwhat was going on, and of Digi's un-   
OL,15,Bcertain future. When the true extent   
OL,16,Bwas clear, he asked me with a heavy    
OL,17,Bheart toEtake Super Page 58 offlineBto 
OL,18,BhelpEsave Digi.B                       
OL,19,B                                       
OL,20,E`````````````````````````````````11/20`
OL,21,             BBy Chris Bell             
OL,22,D]MG    TELETEXT ART SHOWCASE p104      
OL,24,AAboutBUser GuideCTeletext ArtFMainIndex
PN,10612
SC,0012
FL,102,103,104,101,4ff,100
OL,1,U5|j5pp0up`pp0s1z0ppp      W h54  j  
OL,2,U5j5{57js15k!w      W 5$  j  
OL,3,U}~5|4}h|55j }|      Wh2-l|,&  
OL,4,E`````````````````````````````W*7<=mE`
OL,5,BTHE STORY OF SUPER PAGE 58    W!/////  
OL,6,B                                       
OL,7,BIt's a funny thingEgrieving for a Tele-
OL,8,Etext gaming sectionBthat isn't as good 
OL,9,Bas it used to be. It sounds so trivial 
OL,10,Bwhen you put it like that.             
OL,11,B                                       
OL,12,BBut we know what Digi meant to fans,   
OL,13,Band the grief I experienced post-Digi- 
OL,14,Bgate for it was real.                  
OL,15,B                                       
OL,16,BSo it was a shock to receive an email  
OL,17,Bfrom Biffo inENovember 2002,Bunexpected
OL,18,Bas that first one in 1998, announcing  
OL,19,BthatEDigi was back.                    
OL,20,E`````````````````````````````````12/20`
OL,21,             BBy Chris Bell             
OL,22,D]MG    TELETEXT ART SHOWCASE p104      
OL,24,AAboutBUser GuideCTeletext ArtFMainIndex
PN,10613
SC,0013
FL,102,103,104,101,4ff,100
OL,1,U5|j5pp0up`pp0s1z0ppp      W h54  j  
OL,2,U5j5{57js15k!w      W 5$  j  
OL,3,U}~5|4}h|55j }|      Wh2-l|,&  
OL,4,E`````````````````````````````W*7<=mE`
OL,5,BTHE STORY OF SUPER PAGE 58    W!/////  
OL,6,B                                       
OL,7,BDigi was back. Slowly at first, but it 
OL,8,Bwas true. Come itsE10th anniversaryBand
OL,9,Ba perfect tribute fromEAlex Garland,Bit
OL,10,Bit was in ruder health than ever. Yes, 
OL,11,Bdefinitely ruder...                    
OL,12,B                                       
OL,13,BPart of the reason for this, of course,
OL,14,Bwas thatEit was ending.                
OL,15,B                                       
OL,16,BBiffo had decided enough was enough.   
OL,17,BDigi had completed 10 years on air, and
OL,18,Bits humour and personality restored.   
OL,19,BIt was the right time to bow out.      
OL,20,E`````````````````````````````````13/20`
OL,21,             BBy Chris Bell             
OL,22,D]MG    TELETEXT ART SHOWCASE p104      
OL,24,AAboutBUser GuideCTeletext ArtFMainIndex
PN,10614
SC,0014
FL,102,103,104,101,4ff,100
OL,1,U5|j5pp0up`pp0s1z0ppp      W h54  j  
OL,2,U5j5{57js15k!w      W 5$  j  
OL,3,U}~5|4}h|55j }|      Wh2-l|,&  
OL,4,E`````````````````````````````W*7<=mE`
OL,5,BTHE STORY OF SUPER PAGE 58    W!/////  
OL,6,B                                       
OL,7,BDigi came to a glorious end inEMarch   
OL,8,E2003.BBut not before Biffo had "marked"
OL,9,Bthe occasion - onscreen thanks to a    
OL,10,Bcertain "worm", and off it with his    
OL,11,Bleaving drinks.                        
OL,12,B                                       
OL,13,BI felt honoured to be invited along,   
OL,14,Band overcoming a fair amount of social 
OL,15,Banxiety to do, had the best time that  
OL,16,Bnight. The next day? Not so much!      
OL,17,B                                       
OL,18,BThe pubEonly sold beer.BI've hardly    
OL,19,Btouched it since...                    
OL,20,E`````````````````````````````````14/20`
OL,21,             BBy Chris Bell             
OL,22,D]MG    TELETEXT ART SHOWCASE p104      
OL,24,AAboutBUser GuideCTeletext ArtFMainIndex
PN,10616
SC,0016
FL,102,103,104,101,4ff,100
OL,1,U5|j5pp0up`pp0s1z0ppp      W h54  j  
OL,2,U5j5{57js15k!w      W 5$  j  
OL,3,U}~5|4}h|55j }|      Wh2-l|,&  
OL,4,E`````````````````````````````W*7<=mE`
OL,5,BTHE STORY OF SUPER PAGE 58    W!/////  
OL,6,B                                       
OL,7,BPost-Digi, I always intended to keep   
OL,8,Bthe site online, even it wasn't to be  
OL,9,Bupdated again, asEa public serviceBfor 
OL,10,Ball those who wanted it.               
OL,11,B                                       
OL,12,BAnd, apart from a blip when I changed  
OL,13,BISPs around 2006, it did, in one place 
OL,14,Bor another.                            
OL,15,B                                       
OL,16,BThat's where I expected it to stay; a  
OL,17,Brelic of a bygone era. But unbeknownst 
OL,18,Bto me, more than 10 years after Digi   
OL,19,Bended,EBiffo was planning a comeback...
OL,20,E`````````````````````````````````16/20`
OL,21,             BBy Chris Bell             
OL,22,D]MG    TELETEXT ART SHOWCASE p104      
OL,24,AAboutBUser GuideCTeletext ArtFMainIndex
PN,10617
SC,0017
FL,102,103,104,101,4ff,100
OL,1,U5|j5pp0up`pp0s1z0ppp      W h54  j  
OL,2,U5j5{57js15k!w      W 5$  j  
OL,3,U}~5|4}h|55j }|      Wh2-l|,&  
OL,4,E`````````````````````````````W*7<=mE`
OL,5,BTHE STORY OF SUPER PAGE 58    W!/////  
OL,6,B                                       
OL,7,BThe impossible had happened.EDigitiser 
OL,8,Ewas backBon the internet, with Mr Biffo
OL,9,Bat the helm once more.                 
OL,10,B                                       
OL,11,BWhat could I do but come out of retire-
OL,12,Bment and start Super Page 58 up again  
OL,13,Bto cover it?                           
OL,14,B                                       
OL,15,BAfter various abortive attempts over   
OL,16,Bthe years, I finally rebooted the site 
OL,17,BinEFebruary 2018.BWorking on it since  
OL,18,Bthen has been a joyous - if exhausting!
OL,19,B- experience.                          
OL,20,E`````````````````````````````````17/20`
OL,21,             BBy Chris Bell             
