OL,5,BTHE STORY OF SUPER PAGE 58    W!/////  
OL,6,B                                       
OL,7,BI honestly never thought I'd update    
OL,8,BSuper Page 58 ever again. To be doing  
OL,9,Bit now, regularly, becoming theEbest   
OL,10,Eit's ever been,Bis quite head-spinning 
OL,11,Bto think about.                        
OL,12,B                                       
OL,13,BAnd so here we are, atEDigitiser Live. 
OL,14,BThe natural, insane, conclusion for all
OL,15,Bthat has gone before.                  
OL,16,B                                       
OL,17,BThanks for all your support over the   
OL,18,Byears - enjoy Chunky Fringe, Digi, and 
OL,19,Bbeing among your fellow fans.          
