OL,5,BTHE STORY OF SUPER PAGE 58    W!/////  
OL,6,B                                       
OL,7,BOne last thing: why is it calledESuper 
OL,8,EPage 58Bwhen teletext pages are three  
OL,9,Bdigits?                                
OL,10,B                                       
OL,11,BBecause your daddy told me to call it  
OL,12,Bthat, of course!                       
OL,13,B                                       
OL,14,BNot really - it s an old Digi trope    
OL,15,Bwhere things were described as         
OL,16,ESUPER <THING> <NUMBER>.BAnd that's all 
OL,17,Bthe story of that.                     
OL,18,B                                       
