OL,13,ACROAMING THOMAS looks like a gnome.   
OL,14,FBROAMING THOMAS can seem friendly, but
OL,15,Bhe really isn't at all.                
OL,16,ACROAMING THOMAS is just a machine - a 
OL,17,Clittle tin guy with no lungs.          
